{
  "page": "Master of Torrhen's Square",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #DEDEE2; text-align:center;\">Master of Torrhen's Square</th></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Office</th><td>\nRuler of <a href=\"/index.php/Torrhen%27s_Square\" title=\"Torrhen&#39;s Square\">Torrhen's Square</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Region</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">North</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Current Holder</th><td>\nLady <a href=\"/index.php/Eddara_Tallhart\" title=\"Eddara Tallhart\">Eddara Tallhart</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Master of Torrhen's Square</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwdappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> or <b>Lady of Torrhen's Square</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> is the title held by the ruler of <a href=\"/index.php/Torrhen%27s_Square\" title=\"Torrhen&#39;s Square\">Torrhen's Square</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">north</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-master_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-master-5\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Known_Masters_and_Ladies_of_Torrhen.27s_Square\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Known Masters and Ladies of Torrhen's Square</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Master_of_Torrhen%27s_Square&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Master_of_Torrhen%27s_Square&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Helman_Tallhart\" title=\"Helman Tallhart\">Helman Tallhart</a>, the Master of <a href=\"/index.php/Torrhen%27s_Square\" title=\"Torrhen&#39;s Square\">Torrhen's Square</a>, goes with his men to <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a> when <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a> calls the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">northern</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Bannerman\" title=\"Bannerman\">banners</a> in response to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a>'s arrest.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> Helman leaves his brother <a href=\"/index.php/Leobald_Tallhart\" title=\"Leobald Tallhart\">Leobald</a> as <a href=\"/index.php/Castellan\" title=\"Castellan\">castellan</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racokappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Robb names Helman as the commander of the garrison of four hundred archers and swordsmen left at the <a href=\"/index.php/Twins\" title=\"Twins\">Twins</a> to ensure the loyalty of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Master_of_Torrhen%27s_Square&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Edmure_Tully\" title=\"Edmure Tully\">Edmure Tully</a> orders Helman to leave the Twins and join with Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a> to aid in the <a href=\"/index.php/Fall_of_Harrenhal\" title=\"Fall of Harrenhal\">fall of Harrenhal</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> Helman retakes <a href=\"/index.php/Darry\" title=\"Darry\">Castle Darry</a> after a <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Darry\" title=\"Siege of Darry\">small siege</a> with the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">Lannister</a> garrison surrendering after a short period. Roose orders him to torch the castle, kill the captives, and join forces with <a href=\"/index.php/Robett_Glover\" title=\"Robett Glover\">Robett Glover</a> to attack <a href=\"/index.php/Duskendale\" title=\"Duskendale\">Duskendale</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok64.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Rodrik_Cassel\" title=\"Rodrik Cassel\">Rodrik Cassel</a> aids Leobald in fending off the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Dagmer_Cleftjaw\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dagmer Cleftjaw\">Dagmer Cleftjaw</a> in at <a href=\"/index.php/Fight_at_Torrhen%27s_Square\" title=\"Fight at Torrhen&#39;s Square\">fight at Torrhen's Square</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_11-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok56.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-11\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> but Rodrik and Leobald are later killed in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_Winterfell\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Battle at Winterfell\">battle at Winterfell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_12-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok66.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-12\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Master_of_Torrhen%27s_Square&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Helman is killed during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_Duskendale\" title=\"Battle at Duskendale\">battle at Duskendale</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_13-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos37.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-13\">&#91;12&#93;</a></sup> Having been predeceased by his son, <a href=\"/index.php/Benfred_Tallhart\" title=\"Benfred Tallhart\">Benfred</a>, Helman's heir is his daughter, <a href=\"/index.php/Eddara_Tallhart\" title=\"Eddara Tallhart\">Eddara</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Master_of_Torrhen%27s_Square&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Eddara is held captive by the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironmen\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ironmen\">ironmen</a> at Torrhen's Square, following its <a href=\"/index.php/Sack_of_Torrhen%E2%80%99s_Square\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sack of Torrhen’s Square\">capture</a> by Dagmer.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Known_Masters_and_Ladies_of_Torrhen's_Square\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_Masters_and_Ladies_of_Torrhen.27s_Square\">Known Masters and Ladies of Torrhen's Square</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Master_of_Torrhen%27s_Square&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known Masters and Ladies of Torrhen&#039;s Square\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Helman_Tallhart\" title=\"Helman Tallhart\">Helman Tallhart</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Eddara_Tallhart\" title=\"Eddara Tallhart\">Eddara Tallhart</a>, the current Lady of Torrhen's Square.</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Master_of_Torrhen%27s_Square&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-master-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-master_5-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">According to Elio Garcia, <a href=\"/index.php/George_R._R._Martin\" title=\"George R. R. Martin\">George R. R. Martin</a> indicated that <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">northern</a> \"masters\" are similar to <a href=\"/index.php/Southron\" title=\"Southron\">southron</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Landed_knight\" title=\"Landed knight\">landed knights</a>.<a class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://asoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?/topic/34958-the-asoiaf-wiki-thread/&amp;do=findComment&amp;comment=7590729\">[1]</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Master_of_Torrhen%27s_Square&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appen